title: 'Perfect combination of Style & Quality'
body: The quality of these socks is very good comparing the price. Also, the designs and colours of these socks are decent that perfectly suits formal outfits. This pack contains three pairs of free size socks that fits almost everyone.  These are not 100% cotton socks, it's made of cotton and polyester blend with around 73% cotton. Still, it feels very soft and comfortable throughout the day. The best part about the fabric is that it's processed with anti-microbial N9 finish which minimizes any microbial growth in the socks. Although the stitching and exterior finishing is perfect but after few rigid washes, threads will start to come out and will hang from the stitch design all over the socks and that looks really poor. So, better wash it in normal cycle or you will end up damaging the socks.  Overall, these socks are really good in terms of style and price but the thread issue disappointed me a little.  P.S. I review products on amazon to help fellow customers in taking wise decisions and try to ensure that everyone's hard earned money get its full worth. It always makes my day to know that people find my reviews helpful. Feel free to comment for any queries.
